t; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-st=
yle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> issued</a> a=C2=A0<em>new </em>$160 m=
illion=C2=A0convertible bond, yesterday, on a fairly emergency basis, to ra=
ise money to pay back the old one. The <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/34603555.257368/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy=
9lZGdhci9kYXRhLzcwNDU2Mi8wMDAxNjgzMTY4MjQwMDEzNjcvYXZpZF9leDk5MDMuaHRt/607f=
07ceef4b8524a319a23cBfae1c0cf" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscop=
e" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !import=
ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> new one</a> will be considerably mo=
re dilutive=C2=A0and will pay 7% interest instead of 1.25%. Not ideal! To d=
o this, Avid also had to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com=
/click/34603555.257368/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmdvdi9BcmNoaXZlcy9lZGdhci9kYXRh=
LzcwNDU2Mi8wMDAxNjgzMTY4MjQwMDEzNjcvYXZpZF9leDk5MDEuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a3=
19a23cB2e3484bc" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_=
blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bo=
ttom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; =
background-color: #ccc;"> pre-announce its earnings</a> for the last quarte=
r. And because of the forgotten interest, it =E2=80=9C<a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34603555.257368/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2VjLmd=
vdi9peHZpZXdlci9peC5odG1sP2RvYz0vQXJjaGl2ZXMvZWRnYXIvZGF0YS83MDQ1NjIvMDAwMT=
Y4MzE2ODI0MDAxMzU5L2F2aWRfOGsuaHRt/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC036fffa6" itemp=
