=99s a cross-default in its revolving credit agreement. Just a mess.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is a bad oopsie by Avid, which probably s=
hould have put a reminder in its calendar to unrestrict the CUSIP.<a class=
=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-6" style=3D"color: #000000; text-deco=
ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
