<span>[7]</span>
</a> The holder owns =E2=80=9Cat least 25%=E2=80=9D of the bonds (the amoun=
t required to accelerate), and there are=C2=A0$143.75 million of bonds outs=
tanding; 20 points on 25% of $143.75 million is $7.2 million. Plus interest=
.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That=E2=80=99s the thing about efficient marke=
ts, man.=C2=A0<em>You=C2=A0</em>might quite reasonably find section 4.06(e)=
