=C2=A0<em>actually do it=C2=A0</em>have an absolutely bizarre track record =
of messing it up and not making any money on it. It is baffling to me, but =
they put all this work into filing fake press releases and then forget to s=
ell their stock while it=E2=80=99s up. I <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloom=
bergbusiness.com/click/34603555.257368/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9v=
